    {
      "id": "a6402ce3-2e18-4ac1-abf6-93f957ca5801",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "ITS have evolved greatly over the years. ML has definitely played an important role here as it allows for the generation of automatic teaching styles from student characteristics and learning styles. However, a big barrier for the training of ML models is the scarcity of datasets containing student-ITS interactions.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "a6402ce3-2e18-4ac1-abf6-93f957ca5801",
        "parent": {
