    {
      "id": "bfa5ad4b-b82a-4c6d-a6f2-0cdd91f94ff9",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors propose SimStu, built on a Decision Transformer. SimStu is a data simulator that generaties learning behavioral data that is essencial to train ITS models. Results show that SimStu is effective at mimicking real students when it comes to action frequency distribution, thus allowing for the generation of data that could improve the efficiency of ITS training. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
